en.Boxes!: Boxes can be pushed--you can go towards them to force them to move
en.Stopping: If boxes are pushed towards walls, they with you will stop
en.To restart: If you don't think you can win like this, press R to restart the room

zh_cn.\u505c\u6b62: 如果箱子被对着墙推动, 它和你都会停下
zh_cn.\u91cd\u8bd5: 如果你认为你以现在的情况赢不了, 按R来重新开始这个房间
